        <item>
            <title>Apple 推「Reasons to Upgrade」網頁，圖文比較新 iPhone 優點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/reasons-to-upgrade-new-iphone/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=reasons-to-upgrade-new-iphone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/reasons-to-upgrade-new-iphone/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 09:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[升級]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1226633</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>到目前為止 iPhone 最新一代已經到了 iPhone 15。當然不是全部用家都升級到新機，現在還有好多 iPhone 11, 12 的用家。為了吸引這些用家升級，近日 Apple 就新推出「Reasons to Upgrade」（你要升級的原因）網頁，能為你配對舊 iPhone 型號，與新 iPhone 15/ 15 Pro/ 15 Pro Max 不同型號作出直接比較，以圖文解説新 iPhone 值得讓用戶升級的地方。</p><p>Apple 官方網站全新推出<a href="https://www.apple.com/iphone/why-upgrade/?from=iphone-12-mini&amp;to=iphone-15-plus">「Reasons to Upgrade」網頁</a>。這個網頁主要是給舊 iPhone 用家，留意在升級新 iPhone 後可獲得甚麼新功能、硬件升級的地方。舊 iPhone 涵蓋 iPhone 11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/12/12 mini/12 Pro/12 Pro Max。至於新升級的 iPhone 就有 iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032622049-694x317.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="317" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032622049-694x317.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032622049.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>重點是用家可隨意挑選任何型號直接比較。例如挑出 iPhone 12 mini 同 iPhone 15 Plus，兩部機就可拍在一起比較兩者熒幕的大小。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621630-691x580.jpg" alt="" width="691" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621630-691x580.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621630.jpg 1073w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 691px" /></p><p>另外網頁也會介紹其他新機優勝之處，例如 iPhone 15 Plus 在相片拍攝上可有 iPhone 12 mini 最高 4 倍解像度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226637" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621722-694x547.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="547" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621722-694x547.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621722.jpg 1142w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在儲存空間上，Apple 也説明在新 iPhone 上，你可擁有 iPhone 12 mini 超過 2 倍的儲存空間。網頁還有其他兩者比較之下的效能、功能對比，大家可參閲<a href="https://www.apple.com/iphone/why-upgrade/?from=iphone-12-mini&amp;to=iphone-15-plus">官網</a>。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1226638" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621748-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621748-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024032621748.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/iphone/why-upgrade/?from=iphone-12-mini&amp;to=iphone-15-plus">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/25/presto-within-apple/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">無線更新盒內 iPhone 的 iOS 軟件    Apple Store 推最新「Presto within Apple」功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/23/apple-iphone-ai-talks-google-openai-ongoing/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 與 Google、OpenAI 洽談，引入生成式 AI 改善 iOS 功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/tim-cook-visit-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tim Cook 半年兩度訪華，表態支持中國市場及供應鏈</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/reasons-to-upgrade-new-iphone/mobile-phone/">Apple 推「Reasons to Upgrade」網頁，圖文比較新 iPhone 優點</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
