            <title>指未有恪守《數碼市場法》   歐盟宣佈對 Apple、Google、Meta 展開調查</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/eu-probes-apple-google-meta-under-new-digital-law/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=eu-probes-apple-google-meta-under-new-digital-law</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/eu-probes-apple-google-meta-under-new-digital-law/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
